{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id781639bb-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470hh"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"470hh"},"text":"§ 470hh.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Confidentiality of information concerning nature and location of archaeological resources","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id781639bc-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470hh/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Disclosure of information","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Information concerning the nature and location of any archaeological resource for which the excavation or removal requires a permit or other permission under this chapter or under any other provision of Federal law may not be made available to the public under subchapter II of chapter 5 of title 5 or under any other provision of law unless the Federal land manager concerned determines that such disclosure would—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id781639bd-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470hh/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" further the purposes of this chapter or chapter 3125 of title 54, and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id781639be-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470hh/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" not create a risk of harm to such resources or to the site at which such resources are located.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id781639bf-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470hh/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Request for disclosure by Governors","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding the provisions of subsection (a), upon the written request of the Governor of any State, which request shall state—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id781639c0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470hh/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the specific site or area for which information is sought,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id781639c1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470hh/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the purpose for which such information is sought,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id781639c2-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s470hh/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a commitment by the Governor to adequately protect the confidentiality of such information to protect the resource from commercial exploitation,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"the Federal land manager concerned shall provide to the Governor information concerning the nature and location of archaeological resources within the State of the requesting Governor.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id781639c3-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/95/s9"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–95, § 9","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1979-10-31"},"text":"Oct. 31, 1979","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/93/727"},"text":"93 Stat. 727","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/287/s5/d/8"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–287, § 5(d)(8)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/3265"},"text":"128 Stat. 3265","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id781639c4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id781639c5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id781639c6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2014—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/287"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–287","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “chapter 3125 of title 54” for “the Act of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1960-06-27"},"text":"June 27, 1960","children":[],"tail":" ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s469–469c"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 469–469c","children":[],"tail":")” in subsec. (a)(2), was executed by making the substitution in subsec. (a)(1), to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
